'''Ángel Cristo Dordi''' (17 October 1944 in [[Huelva]] – 4 May 2010 in [[Madrid]]) was a Spanish circus performer.

On 3 May 2010 he was admitted to the University Hospital of Alcorcón after suffering multiple cardiac arrests. He died on 4 May as a result of a final heart attack.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.publico.es/televisionygente/310013/fallece/angel/cristo |title=Fallece a los 66 años el domador Ángel Cristo |publisher=Publico.es |date= |accessdate=2010-05-30}}</ref>

